Maintainer: Yann Richet <yann.richet@irsn.fr>
Description: Interface to 'libKriging' 'C++' library
        <https://github.com/libKriging> that should provide most
        standard Kriging / Gaussian process regression features (like
        in 'DiceKriging', 'kergp' or 'RobustGaSP' packages).
        'libKriging' relies on Armadillo linear algebra library (Apache
        2 license) by Conrad Sanderson, 'lbfgsb_cpp' is a 'C++' port
        around by Pascal Have of 'lbfgsb' library (BSD-3 license) by
        Ciyou Zhu, Richard Byrd, Jorge Nocedal and Jose Luis Morales
        used for hyperparameters optimization.
